    "'Confirm' does not feature in the top ten collocates for earlier time periods, which raises questions about why this particular structure is employed now and how it may impact the perception of ChatGPT as an active agent in the Twitter discourse.",
    "Tweets suggest that more users may be utilising ChatGPT to answer questions about itself, raising questions about the legitimacy of responses and the attribution of responsibility, accountability, and blame if something were to go wrong.",
